  <brief_title>Laryngeal Injuries After Removal of the Tracheal Tube: A Comparison Between Sevoflurane and Propofol</brief_title>
  <official_title>Laryngeal Injuries After Removal of the Tracheal Tube: A Comparison Between Anesthesia With Sevoflurane and Intravenous Anesthesia With Propofol A Randomized, Prospective, Controlled Trial</official_title>
  <sponsors>
